            . On the 19th of October the prisoner hired this stanhope for one month, at 3l. a month - it was worth 30l.; it has never been returned.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. When I hired it I asked you the price, and you said it would be 30l. if I kept it. Witness. He never said a word about the price.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-111-person964">
