            . I found the stanhope at Mr. Robinson's, advertised for sale; it had not been returned - I have not received a farthing for the hire.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-111-person965">
                  HENRY 
                  AGATE
               <interp inst="t18310908-111-person965" type="surname" value="AGATE"></interp>
