                     <interp inst="t18310908-111-person965" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a clerk at Robinson's repository. The prisoner brought this stanhope on the 26th of October, for sale; I advanced him 10l. on it - it has not been sold; it is now in our possession - the prisoner has not applied for it.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I hired it to let out; the price was to be 30l. if I bought it - I have tickets to prove it was let out on hire - when I was taken I was allowed three days to settle this, but could not find friends.</p>
